Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,fx,{\an8\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}おやすみ異世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:19.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,fx,{\an8\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}さようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:19.07,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\an2\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}入睡轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.89,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\an2\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}只要在想着你
