Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:37.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\an2\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}待治愈了厌恶与伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:41.80,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\an2\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}再看看和平的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:49.80,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\an2\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}唱着羽衣草啊 羽衣草
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:56.69,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\an2\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}重整我奄奄一息的心灵
